{"tid":1764302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推!!! 有關今日既遊行sss!!!","createTime":"2019-12-01T04:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T05:09:35.000Z","uid":113705,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d49d88b4a425d5ce86f50d27bbd46ee6f80dcdfd","tid":1764302,"uid":113705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"不喜勿插，我覺得今日可以全程和理非，等班狗無藉口唔批下星期既民陣遊行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班和理非已經好耐無參與過，最近出得黎抗爭既都算係勇武，班和理非根本無咩機會參與。我覺得要團結一致，再次黎多個百萬大遊行，話比政府知，香港人要反抗，有幾百萬人企出黎對抗呢個政權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下星期民陣仲申請緊大遊行，而今日d警察又批晒所有不反，所以我覺得今日全程和理非，等班警察無藉口唔批下星期既遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎多次百萬大遊行，香港人要團結，要反抗! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3be4d5605434b1651b9814831e4a25bb1fd3697","tid":1764302,"uid":113705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a7dfd05807524191325b0cc6a15346bf08e2e5ae","tid":1764302,"uid":113705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"083f254e93209a4192b58824fe6a40c733bfb2e6","tid":1764302,"uid":113705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"200132ef4402327c460b154521d0958bc02aea82","tid":1764302,"uid":113705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"f438303af4f5b12d05400898887415f697f0054b","tid":1764302,"uid":113705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"473f0fdfd4d4492e7411c38922788bbce0f1b62f","tid":1764302,"uid":113705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB